quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  21,36,"Na wanapokuona wale waliokufuru, hawakufanyi wewe isipokuwa ni kitu cha masihara tu, (wakisema): Je, huyu ndiye anayeitaja miungu yenu? Na hali wao wanakufuru kumkumbuka Arrahman (Mwingi wa rehema)!",""
  21,37,"Mwanadamu ameumbwa na haraka. Nitawaonyesha Ishara zangu. Basi msiniharakishe.",""
  21,38,"Na wanasema: Ahadi hii itatokea lini, ikiwa nyinyi ni wakweli?",""
  21,39,"Lau wangelijua wale waliokufuru wakati ambao hawatauzuia Moto kwenye nyuso zao wala migongo yao, na wala hawatanusuriwa!",""
  21,40,"Bali itawafikia kwa ghafla, na itawashitua na wala hawataweza kuirudisha, wala hawatapewa muhula!",""
  21,41,"Na Mitume walio kabla yako walikwishadhihakiwa. Kwa hivyo wale waliowafanyia masihara yaliwafika yale waliyokuwa wakiyafanyia dhihaka.",""
  21,42,"Sema: Ni nani anayewalinda usiku na mchana mbali na Arrahmani (Mwingi wa rehema)? Bali wao wanapuuza kumkumbuka Mola wao Mlezi.",""
  21,43,"Au wao wanao miungu watakaoweza kuwakinga kutokana nasi? Hao hawawezi kujinusuru wao wenyewe, wala hawatalindwa kutokana nasi!",""
  21,44,"Bali tuliwastarehesha hawa na baba zao mpaka umri ukawa mrefu kwao. Je, hawaoni ya kwamba Sisi tunaijia ardhi tukiipunguza kutokea kwenye ncha zake? Basi je, hao ndio watashinda?",""
